org.conqat.lib.commons.serialization.utils

Class SerializedClassFieldMigrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.conqat.lib.commons.serialization.utils.SerializedClassFieldMigrator

  • public class SerializedClassFieldMigrator
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class to consistently migrate field names of a SerializedClass with their corresponding field values in all SerializedObject of the SerializedClass.
